As earlier reported by Sundiata Post, just few weeks after Triple MG boss, Ubi Franklin announced the birth of his 3rd child, another baby – a 4th from the 4th lady – is on it’s way. Triple MG boss, Ubi Franklin is expecting his fourth child with a U.S-based Nigerian businesswoman, Sandra Iheuwa. But all is not well. Sandra has taken to her Instagram to call him out for Fraud and manipulation. In the post she revealed how they met and how he tricked her into giving him a loan. See her post below.